channel.title: Strange Error when others try and get on my server
channel.description: O.K... im not a normal noob asking where client.java is or anything, i know the basics. i have no-ip DUC downloaded, i use Testscape, i know both my COMPUTER IP and my INTERNET IP.. and my SERVER IP is: nurbiescape.no-ip.org. ok. my brother can get on my server, so can my cousin, but when other people try and get on, they say they cant get on.. real weird. everything is installed (im pretty sure) and i have RunServer going, but it doesnt even show them trying to log in. Any hosters know whats wrong with my server?[br][size=1]Posted at: December 16, 2006, 08:59:14 PM[/size][hr]anyone? :D :D :) :|
